---
description: Keep CLI (Typer/Rich) in cli/; core logic in src; no CLI imports in core.
globs: "src/puzzletree/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Layering

- **Core logic** (app, rag, datasets, config): Pure logic—no Typer, Rich, or `cli` imports. Inputs/outputs are data (paths, dicts, dataclasses).
- **cli/**: Commands call into core modules; all Typer/Rich/UX live here.
- **Direction**: `cli` → core. Never the reverse.
